OL,3,C'Vital' bus service for cancer
OL,4,Cpatients found not to be 'best value
OL,5,Cfor money'
OL,7,FHealth and Care Jersey (HCJ), which
OL,8,Fallocates the #56,600 annually,
OL,9,Fdecided to discontinue the service
OL,10,Ffollowing a review which found that it
OL,11,Fwas not the "best value for money".
OL,13,FHCJ also found it was more
OL,14,F"economical" for patients to use HCJ-
OL,15,Ffunded taxis instead, as they can be
OL,16,Fused anytime, whereas the bus was on a
OL,17,Ftimetabled service.
