OL,3,C'Vital' bus service for cancer
OL,4,Cpatients found not to be 'best value
OL,5,Cfor money'
OL,7,F"All patients who currently use the
OL,8,FDaisy Bus Service will be made aware
OL,9,Fof their new travel arrangements when
OL,10,Fthe service discontinues."
OL,12,FThe termination will also impact
OL,13,Fpatients from the Isle of Wight who
OL,14,Fare staying in mainland hotels and use
OL,15,Fthe service.
OL,17,FHowever, in a joint statement, Wessex
OL,18,FCancer Support and University Hospital
OL,19,FSouthampton NHS Foundation Trust said
OL,20,Fthere would be alternative support to
OL,21,Fbe used by cancer patients.
