OL,3,C'Vital' bus service for cancer
OL,4,Cpatients found not to be 'best value
OL,5,Cfor money'
OL,7,FThey said: "We want to reassure
OL,8,Fpatients that support remains
OL,9,Favailable through NHS schemes for
OL,10,Fthose who meet eligibility criteria.
OL,12,F"This includes help with travel costs
OL,13,Fthrough the NHS Healthcare Travel
OL,14,FCosts Scheme (HTCS) and access to Non-
OL,15,FEmergency Patient Transport Services
OL,16,F(NEPTS) for eligible patients.
OL,18,F"The Daisy Bus service between
OL,19,FPortsmouth ferry terminal and Queen
OL,20,FAlexandra Hospital in Portsmouth will
OL,21,Fcontinue at this time.
